```plantuml
@startuml Scientific-Computing-Lab-NRCN_compar

actor User

participant "HTML/CSS\nJinja2, JavaScript/jQuery\nGUI" as GUI
participant "Compiler Abstraction" as Compiler
participant "Parallelization Tools\n(Cetus, Autopar, Par4All)" as ParallelTools
participant "Compilation Parameters" as CompParams
participant "Code Instrumentation" as CodeInstr
participant "Runtime Analysis" as RuntimeAnalysis
participant "Slurm Job Management" as Slurm
participant "Output Validation" as OutputValidation
database "MongoDB" as MongoDB

User -> GUI: Interact with GUI
GUI -> Compiler: Select Compiler
Compiler -> ParallelTools: Integrate Parallelization Tool
ParallelTools -> CompParams: Generate Compilation Parameters
CompParams -> CodeInstr: Instrument Code
CodeInstr -> Slurm: Submit Job
Slurm -> MongoDB: Store Results
MongoDB -> RuntimeAnalysis: Fetch Results
RuntimeAnalysis -> OutputValidation: Validate Output
OutputValidation -> User: Display Results

@enduml
```